location.fullValue: Odessa Plan, The Preserve at Singing Hills

data.description: Welcome to your retreat on a beautiful, shaded 1.52-acre property. This gem offers a great opportunity to purchase in this stunning neighborhood at a more affordable price. It has so much to offer including a high vaulted ceiling living room with wood beams, an island kitchen with granite tops, and stainless appliances. Laminate and tile flooring (no carpet) give this home a luxurious feel. Unwind in the cozy master suite with outdoor access, split vanity, and a separate jetted tub and tile shower. With a neighbor on only one side and the community park on the other, this property feels like it goes on forever. Enjoy the outdoor features with a wrap-around front porch, back deck, and a two-car detached garage. This property combines the charm of rural living with the convenience of the city.
